{"tid":1305473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係要諗點樣令運動唔失焦，係去諗點樣減少影響","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:36:51.000Z","uid":196536,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92ce2bd89eadf28a254e2553af2f7c2914ce5acf","tid":1305473,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:52:30.000Z","msg":"大佬，全港運動，又無大台<br />\n失焦係一定會出現<br />\n只係時間問題<br />\n要佢唔出現係無可能<br />\n好似之前巴打一個比喻咁<br />\n香港接受緊癌症治療<br />\n治療會有副作用<br />\n失焦咪係果個副作用囉<br />\n<br />\n香港人記住<br />\n呢場仗最大既敵人唔係個政權唔係克警<br />\n係我地自己每一個人<br />\n呢場仗要贏<br />\n其實係睇我地硬唔硬淨<br />\n有無長期抗戰臥薪嘗膽既心架咋<br />\n我唔敢話呢場仗打落贏硬<br />\n但呢場仗，我100%同你講係有得打既<br />\n加油啦大家<br />\n共勉之！"},{"pid":"129093ab75f936538cb0feb3907fb1211a5f654d","tid":1305473,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:08:46.000Z","msg":"Let&rsquo;s win this"},{"pid":"1945fa7e78bfee78d733ae1c80a0de6fcd01f9b0","tid":1305473,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"129093ab75f936538cb0feb3907fb1211a5f654d","tid":1305473,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:08:46.000Z","msg":"Let&rsquo;s win this"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:22:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d7097ea6c915e405c2d7b31c434df1e4388a644c","tid":1305473,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d8f0440530a13c5d61c74f321acbb0c2bbd0ac8d","tid":1305473,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKniOCc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKniOCc.png&h=16423938&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmiFhvx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmiFhvx.png&h=0870e1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aCMjx3T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2